name: HOOVABIKE NEOXA.Hg02
description:
NEOXA.Hg02 was remodeled and flown by Seken Geli. It is most effectively used as a recon ship and adept at camouflaging.

NEOXA.Hg02 was about 2.7m long / 2m wide, weighing 7.2 tons. Most of Nova built use APS (Automatic Psychomotor System), that designed for the Geli tribe. Several additional features of NEOXA.Hg02 includes Twin Lure Rod, Sky-Gazer, Anti-Missile Devices, and Camo Cloak.

Manufactured in year 5, Geli Exo Planet.
